 Retail



Meet challenges with energy efficiency.

Whether you’re running a boutique or a bike repair shop, your business has unique operational challenges and power requirements. Let the NRG family of companies meet those challenges with energy solutions.

As a Texas-based company, Reliant is part of the community. We live and work in Texas and know how to serve your unique needs. With Reliant, you’ll get access to more than just electricity. You get your own team of energy experts armed with the right products and solutions to help you run your operation. Plus, we're backed by NRG, the largest independent power producer in the U.S.
Case studies
Read about how we work with our ambassadors to create powerful companies.

Athlete Training + Health (ATH)›
Lighting Etc.›
Products and services

Take a closer look at the products and services available for your business from the NRG family of companies.
Electricity Plans
Reliant provides a wide variety of plans that fit your needs.
Security by Reliant 
Protect your business 24/7 with a customizable security system. 
Business Surge Protect
Get peace of mind knowing some of your electronics will be covered in the event of an electrical surge.
HVAC Tune-Up
Keep up with the demands of unpredictable Texas weather and schedule an AC or Heater check up.
Generators
Keep your lights on during power outages with a backup generator.





Terms, conditions and other restrictions

Business Surge Protect is provided by Allied Warranty. HVAC maintenance and commercial generator offer, installation and maintenance are provided by Reliant Energy Retail Services LLC TACLB23923E | MPL17217 Rickey Tyler | TECL32274. Regulated by the Texas Department of Licensing & Regulation, P.O. Box 12157, Austin, TX 78711, 1-800-803-9202, 512-463-6599, and Texas State Board of Plumbing Examiners, P.O. Box 4200, Austin, TX 78765, 1-800-845-6584, 512-936-5249. Goal Zero products are offered by Goal Zero LLC. All of these companies are wholly owned subsidiaries of NRG Energy, Inc.        










