ShareOverviewSummaryReliant Energy Retail Services, Llc has worked on twenty-seven contracts worth $59.2 million USD in obligations from the federal government since FY2007. In its latest active fiscal year (2014), the organization received a total of $6 million USD in obligations.The principal agencies it has contracted with are the Department of Veterans Affairs, National Aeronautics and Space Administration, and General Services Administration.

